
This is my little game based on Duck Hunt!

You loose a live, when a ship hits the other side of the screen!
Try to shoot them, with the left mouse button
and reach the highest possible score!

Black ship will increase your score by 5.
White ships are your allies and will decrease it by 10 so be careful!

Made by NiffelStudios [Epitech 2019]
All rights included lol

